title: Have a Different Spirit | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Have a Different Spirit | Joel Osteen
description:
Too many people go around negative, thinking they'll never reach their dreams. But God put a different spirit inside of us. When you look for opportunities to be grateful and positive about life, God will take care of getting you where you need to be. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
